---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="InnovateZ | About Us" description="Learn how InnovateZ builds digital products with clarity, speed, and care.">
	<section class="pt-40 md:pt-48 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop max-w-container-max mx-auto w-full">
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
			<div class="lg:col-span-7">
				<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">
					About InnovateZ
				</span>
				<h1 class="font-display-lg text-headline-lg-mobile sm:text-headline-lg md:text-display-lg leading-tight text-on-background mb-6 text-balance">
					We build products that move fast and still feel precise.
				</h1>
				<p class="font-body-lg text-body-md sm:text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl">
					InnovateZ is a product engineering studio focused on practical software.
					We combine modern design systems, reliable architecture, and a lean delivery
					style so teams can launch with confidence and keep improving without losing
					momentum.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="lg:col-span-5 glass-panel rounded-xl border border-white/10 p-8">
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
					<div class="rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-5 border border-white/5">
						<div class="text-primary font-headline-md text-3xl mb-2">10+</div>
						<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm font-body-md">Years of product thinking packed into a modern delivery process.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-5 border border-white/5">
						<div class="text-primary font-headline-md text-3xl mb-2">3x</div>
						<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm font-body-md">Focus on speed, clarity, and long-term maintainability.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-5 border border-white/5 sm:col-span-2">
						<div class="text-primary font-headline-md text-3xl mb-2">Product-first</div>
						<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm font-body-md">Every decision starts with the user experience and ends with a stable implementation.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-20 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop max-w-container-max mx-auto w-full">
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
			<div class="glass-panel rounded-xl p-8 border border-white/10">
				<h2 class="font-headline-md text-2xl text-on-background mb-4">Mission</h2>
				<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body-md leading-7">
					Ship useful digital products quickly, then refine them with disciplined
					engineering so they stay fast, understandable, and ready to scale.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="glass-panel rounded-xl p-8 border border-white/10">
				<h2 class="font-headline-md text-2xl text-on-background mb-4">Approach</h2>
				<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body-md leading-7">
					We keep the stack simple, the interfaces intentional, and the handoff clean
					so teams can own the product after launch without friction.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="glass-panel rounded-xl p-8 border border-white/10">
				<h2 class="font-headline-md text-2xl text-on-background mb-4">What We Value</h2>
				<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body-md leading-7">
					Clear communication, thoughtful UX, reliable delivery, and systems that are
					easy to maintain long after the first launch.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="pb-24 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop max-w-container-max mx-auto w-full">
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-stretch">
			<div class="lg:col-span-5 glass-panel rounded-xl p-8 border border-white/10">
				<h2 class="font-headline-md text-3xl text-on-background mb-4">How we work</h2>
				<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body-md leading-7 mb-6">
					We design around the product outcome first, then build in small, visible
					steps so the team can validate direction early and avoid expensive resets.
				</p>
				<ul class="space-y-4 text-on-surface-variant font-body-md">
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span> Discovery that clarifies scope and priorities.</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span> Interface systems that stay consistent across pages.</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span> Engineering that balances speed with maintainability.</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="lg:col-span-7 rounded-xl bg-linear-to-br from-surface-container-low to-surface-container-high p-8 md:p-12 border border-white/10 relative overflow-hidden">
				<div class="absolute inset-0 tech-grid opacity-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
				<div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl">
					<span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-white/10 rounded-full font-label-sm text-label-sm text-on-background mb-6 tracking-widest uppercase">Why clients come back</span>
					<h2 class="font-display-lg text-3xl md:text-5xl text-on-background mb-6">Because the product stays usable after launch.</h2>
					<p class="font-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-8">
						The goal is not just delivery. It is building a foundation that teams can
						evolve confidently as requirements change.
					</p>
					<a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary text-on-primary font-label-sm text-label-sm font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(255,233,185,0.3)] transition-all" href="/#contact">
						Start a project <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary">arrow_forward</span>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>